      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a cooperative stance, but the transition is looking complex. Some of our analysts are concerned that the \"equity\" focus might actually cause a drop in total yields. Based on your data, do you honestly believe a decentralized approach for smallholders can maintain current global caloric levels, or are we looking at a massive supply deficit?",
